	(text "ALL ACTIVE LOW SIGNALS ARE IDENTIFIED WITH THE LETTER N.\nFor instance, FMC_NWE is the Write Enable (WE) active low (N)\nsignal from the FMC bus.\n\nINTERNAL PULL-UP RESISTORS OF THE STM32H7 shall be used to\nkeep these signals high when not used."
